song.title: Jesus We Enthrone You
song.lyrics:
[V] .G Em Jesus, we enthrone You .C D We proclaim You are King .Em Bm Standing here, in the midst of Us .C Am Dsus D We raise You up with our praise
[C] .C Bm Em D And as we worship build, Your throne .C D G Em And as we worship build, Your throne .C D G Em And as we worship build, Your throne .Am Dsus D G C D Come Lord Jesus, and take Your place
